# Separate Template and Style Files

- Never use inline `template` or `styles` in `@Component`. Always use `templateUrl` and `styleUrl`.
- Every component must have a co-located `.component.html` and `.component.css` file.
- Use `templateUrl: './{name}.component.html'` and `styleUrl: './{name}.component.css'`.

```typescript
// BAD
@Component({
  selector: 'app-example',
  template: `<div>inline</div>`,
  styles: `:host { display: block; }`,
})

// GOOD
@Component({
  selector: 'app-example',
  templateUrl: './example.component.html',
  styleUrl: './example.component.css',
})
```
